{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Class","role":"symbol","title":"WeakRef","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:10GLibObject7WeakRefC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"WeakRef"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"WeakRef"}]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"WeakRef","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GWeakRef"},{"type":"text","text":" can either be empty (i.e. point to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), or point to an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"object for as long as at least one “strong” reference to that object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"exists. Before the object’s "},{"code":"GObjectClass.dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method is called,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"every "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/WeakRef"},{"type":"text","text":" associated with becomes empty (i.e. points to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Like "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Value","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/WeakRef","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be statically allocated, stack- or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"heap-allocated, or embedded in larger structures.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":